# SAP Security Transactions & Tools

## 👤 User Administration
- **SU01** → User creation and maintenance  
- **SU10** → Mass user maintenance  
- **SUIM** → User and authorization reports  
- **USR21 (Table)** → Identify user via email (PERSNUMBER)  

## 🔐 Role & Authorization Management
- **PFCG** → Role creation and authorization management  
- **PFCG_MASS_COLL_ASSIGN** → Mass role/profile assignment  
- **SU24** → Default authorization objects for transactions  
- **SU25** → Authorization adjustment (ECC → S/4HANA)  
- **SU21** → Authorization object maintenance  
- **SU53** → Authorization error analysis  
- **AGR_1251 (Table)** → Role authorization data  
- **AGR_USERS (Table)** → Role assignment to users  
- **AGR_DEFINE (Table)** → Role definition details  
- **AGR_AGRS (Table)** → Composite roles structure  

## 🔍 Tables & Data Analysis
- **SE16 / SE16N** → Table data analysis  
- **USR05 (Table)** → User parameters  
- **TSTC (Table)** → Transaction codes  
- **ZSDT059 (Custom Table)** → Custom business data  

## 🔎 Audit & Trace
- **SM20** → Security audit log  
- **SM19** → Audit configuration / Firefighter setup  
- **STAUTHTRACE** → Advanced authorization trace  
- **ST01** → Authorization/system trace  
- **USMM_OLD** → Audit/license data  

## 🛡️ GRC & Access Control
- **/n/SAST/START** → GRC Access  
- **IMA11** → Risk analysis / compliance  
- **LRFMD** → Data collector  

## 🌐 SAP Fiori & Gateway
- **/UI2/FLPD_CUST** → Fiori catalog configuration  
- **/UI2/FLPCM_CUST** → Fiori content manager  
- **/UI2/FLP** → Fiori Launchpad  
- **/UI2/GW_APPS_LOG** → Fiori app logs  
- **/UI2/GW_ERR_LOG** → Gateway error logs  
- **/IWFND/ERROR_LOG** → General gateway logs  
- **/IWFND/MAINT_SERVICE** → Activate OData services  
- **/UI2/GW_SYS_ALIAS** → System alias configuration  

## 🔗 Integration & Business Objects
- **BP** → Business Partner management  
- **BP_USER_GEN** → Generate user from BP  
- **RMPS_SET_SUBSTITUTE** → User delegation (S/4 scenario)  

## 🚀 Transport & Development
- **SE10 / SE01** → Transport request management  
- **STMS / STMS_QA** → Transport management system  
- **SE93** → Transaction code maintenance  
- **SE37** → Function module execution  
- **SA38** → Program execution  

## ⚙️ System & Basis Administration
- **SM21** → System logs  
- **ST22** → Dump analysis  
- **SM37** → Job monitoring  
- **SM04** → Active user sessions  
- **AL12** → Table buffer monitoring  
- **RZ10** → Profile parameters (instance)  
- **RZ11** → Dynamic parameter changes  

## 🌍 Services & Web
- **SICF** → Service activation  
- **sap-ui-tech-hint=GUI** → Force GUI rendering in Fiori  

## 🧠 Additional Tools & Reports
- **PROFGEN_CORR_REPORT_2 / PRGN_CORR2** → Role/profile corrections  
- **TOST** → SAPscript texts  
- **/PGT*** → Custom search (environment-specific)  

---

## 💡 Notes
These transactions were used in SAP ECC and S/4HANA environments during daily consulting activities, including access management, audit support, Fiori configuration and system troubleshooting.
